er\">\n\t\t\t<h1 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Related posts<span style=\"color:#DE5E91\">.<\/span><\/h1>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ed753f6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"ed753f6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f375804 elementor-grid-eael-col-2 elementor-grid-tablet-eael-col-2 elementor-grid-mobile-eael-col-1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-eael-post-grid\" data-id=\"f375804\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;eael_post_grid_columns&quot;:&quot;eael-col-2&quot;,&quot;eael_post_grid_columns_tablet&quot;:&quot;eael-col-2&quot;,&quot;eael_post_grid_columns_mobile&quot;:&quot;eael-col-1&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"eael-post-grid.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<div id=\"eael-post-grid-f375804\" class=\"eael-post-grid-container\">\n            <div class=\"eael-post-grid eael-post-appender eael-post-appender-f375804 eael-post-grid-style-default\" data-layout-mode=\"masonry\"><article class=\"eael-grid-post eael-post-grid-column\" data-id=\"7843\">\n        <div class=\"eael-grid-post-holder\">\n            <div class=\"eael-grid-post-holder-inner\"><div class=\"eael-entry-wrapper\"><header class=\"eael-entry-header\"><h2 class=\"eael-entry-title\"><a\n                        class=\"eael-grid-post-link\"\n                        href=\"https:\/\/diegovz.com\/en\/blog\/what-product-design-really-is\"\n                        title=\"What Product Design really is\">What Product Design really is<\/a><\/h2><\/header><div class=\"eael-entry-content\">\n                        <div class=\"eael-grid-post-excerpt\"><p>How many times have you been told that a Product Designer has to be the voice of the user? If so, you've been told half the story...<\/p><a\n                            href=\"https:\/\/diegovz.com\/en\/blog\/what-product-design-really-is\"\n                            class=\"eael-post-elements-readmore-btn\">Leer m\u00e1s<\/a><\/div>\n                    <\/div><div class=\"eael-entry-footer\"><div class=\"eael-entry-meta\"><span class=\"eael-posted-on\"><time datetime=\"June 20, 2021\">June 20, 2021<\/time><\/span><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/article><article class=\"eael-grid-post eael-post-grid-column\" data-id=\"8589\">\n        <div class=\"eael-grid-post-holder\">\n            <div class=\"eael-grid-post-holder-inner\"><div class=\"eael-entry-wrapper\"><header class=\"eael-entry-header\"><h2 class=\"eael-entry-title\"><a\n                        class=\"eael-grid-post-link\"\n                        href=\"https:\/\/diegovz.com\/blog\/lo-que-realmente-es-el-product-design\"\n                        title=\"Lo que realmente es el Product Design\">Lo que realmente es el Product Design<\/a><\/h2><\/header><div class=\"eael-entry-content\">\n                        <div class=\"eael-grid-post-excerpt\"><p>\u00bfCu\u00e1ntas veces te han dicho que un Product Designer tiene que ser (s\u00f3lo) la voz del usuario? Si es as\u00ed, te contaron la mitad de la historia..<\/p><a\n                            href=\"https:\/\/diegovz.com\/blog\/lo-que-realmente-es-el-product-design\"\n                            class=\"eael-post-elements-readmore-btn\">Leer m\u00e1s<\/a><\/div>\n                    <\/div><div class=\"eael-entry-footer\"><div class=\"eael-entry-meta\"><span class=\"eael-posted-on\"><time datetime=\"June 20, 2021\">June 20, 2021<\/time><\/span><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/article><article class=\"eael-grid-post eael-post-grid-column\" data-id=\"7643\">\n        <div class=\"eael-grid-post-holder\">\n            <div 