os las diferencias entre un Grid de 8pt y otro de 10pt, y finalmente veremos cu\u00e1l deber\u00edamos usar.<\/p><a\n                            href=\"https:\/\/diegovz.com\/blog\/grid-8pt-vs-10pt\"\n                            class=\"eael-post-elements-readmore-btn\">Leer m\u00e1s<\/a><\/div>\n                    <\/div><div class=\"eael-entry-footer\"><div class=\"eael-entry-meta\"><span class=\"eael-posted-on\"><time datetime=\"May 27, 2021\">May 27, 2021<\/time><\/span><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/article><article class=\"eael-grid-post eael-post-grid-column\" data-id=\"6894\">\n        <div class=\"eael-grid-post-holder\">\n            <div class=\"eael-grid-post-holder-inner\"><div class=\"eael-entry-wrapper\"><header class=\"eael-entry-header\"><h2 class=\"eael-entry-title\"><a\n                        class=\"eael-grid-post-link\"\n                        href=\"https:\/\/diegovz.com\/blog\/ley-de-hicks\"\n                        title=\"Ley de Hicks\">Ley de Hicks<\/a><\/h2><\/header><div class=\"eael-entry-content\">\n                        <div class=\"eael-grid-post-excerpt\"><p>La Ley de Hick dice que el tiempo que hay que invertir para tomar una decisi\u00f3n se ve incrementado por el n\u00famero de opciones disponibles.<\/p><a\n                            href=\"https:\/\/diegovz.com\/blog\/ley-de-hicks\"\n                            class=\"eael-post-elements-readmore-btn\">Leer m\u00e1s<\/a><\/div>\n                    <\/div><div class=\"eael-entry-footer\"><div class=\"eael-entry-meta\"><span class=\"eael-posted-on\"><time datetime=\"May 24, 2021\">May 24, 2021<\/time><\/span><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/article><article class=\"eael-grid-post eael-post-grid-column\" data-id=\"6935\">\n        <div class=\"eael-grid-post-holder\">\n            <div class=\"eael-grid-post-holder-inner\"><div class=\"eael-entry-wrapper\"><header class=\"eael-entry-header\"><h2 class=\"eael-entry-title\"><a\n      